<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200808/36ca990dc443483394fe49647b8a632c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲张代友作品欣赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200808/6200b0eb86be4c729937f62ed69ae750.png" max-width="600" /></p>
