<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200808/9a59a02994a64eefb2281051c7f8ec3c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲张代友作品欣赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200808/3e0b34bbdef34edebba78eff2b19d44a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
